NEW JERSEY DIVISION OF CHILD PROTECTION AND PERMANENCY, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
S.S., Defendant-Petitioner,
and
A.H., Defendant. In the Matter of the Guardianship of S.A.R.H., a Minor-Respondent. C-1051 September Term 2018
082551 Supreme Court of New Jersey. July 11, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-002388-17 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
